data.description: Immense pie-shaped pool-sized lot! Open and versatile floorplan includes a study or 4th bedroom and a dining room that can be another living area! The private master has room for a sitting area that overlooks the backyard. The master bathroom includes an oversized shower, a large linen closet, walk-in closet, & separate sinks. The spacious kitchen is perfect for entertaining with the gas range that makes cooking a breeze! Serve the food for your guests on the long island bar that separates the great room. Everyone can relax in the great room which includes the wall of windows and room for the largest of entertainment cabinetry. The pie-shaped cul-de-sac corner backyard is just awaiting your design plans.
